      "text": "Responder on Quora claims that their are two historically distinct Monsantos -- one a chemical company, and one a seed company. Going through the Wikipedia article, it's really impossible to say whether it is true or false. The greater lesson is perhaps that we talk about companies as if they were individuals with a history, but in a world of spinoffs, mergers, and hopscotch CEOs the definition of \"what companies did in the past\" is complex and far from predictive. [http://www.quora.com/Is-Monsanto-evil html]"
